{"doc":{"body":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"ue7b25a8d\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">点击劫持（Clickjacking）</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 是一种恶意攻击技术，攻击者通过透明或半透明的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">&lt;iframe&gt;</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 将目标网站覆盖在看似无害的页面上，诱使用户在不知情的情况下点击按钮或链接，从而执行非本意的操作，例如点赞、转账、授权等。</span></p><h3 id=\"uxgcc\"><span class=\"ne-text\">攻击原理</span></h3><ol class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"uce8dfd4e\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">攻击者构建一个恶意页面，并通过 CSS 将目标网站（例如 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">bank.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">）嵌入到一个透明的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">&lt;iframe&gt;</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中。</span></li><li id=\"ub46d68b9\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">该透明层对准用户可见的诱饵元素（如“点击领奖”按钮）。</span></li><li id=\"u9325758c\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">用户点击诱饵时，实际点击的是下方透明的目标网站界面，从而触发了未经授权的操作。</span></li></ol><h3 id=\"scZEu\"><span class=\"ne-text\">防范方法</span></h3><h4 id=\"FYFhM\"><span class=\"ne-text\">1. 使用 HTTP 响应头</span></h4><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"uddc5431d\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">X-Frame-Options</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">（传统方案）  </span></li></ul><ul class=\"ne-list-wrap\"><ul ne-level=\"1\" class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u8c0a732f\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">DENY</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：禁止所有页面以 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">&lt;iframe&gt;</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 形式嵌入。  </span></li><li id=\"ub107adac\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">SAMEORIGIN</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：仅允许同源页面嵌入。  </span></li><li id=\"u324f5207\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">示例：</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN</span></code></li></ul></ul><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u08abbd21\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">（现代 CSP 方案，推荐）  </span></li></ul><ul class=\"ne-list-wrap\"><ul ne-level=\"1\" class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u832f3de1\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">可以更精细地控制允许嵌入的父页面。  </span></li><li id=\"ube877a9c\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">示例：</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors 'self' https://trusted.com;</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">  </span></li><li id=\"u8d98e3b5\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">该指令支持多个源，比 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">X-Frame-Options</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 更灵活，优先级更高。</span></li></ul></ul><h4 id=\"Ua6to\"><span class=\"ne-text\">2. 前端 frame busting（辅助防御）</span></h4><p id=\"u114475ad\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在页面中添加 JavaScript 代码，尝试检测并跳出 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">&lt;iframe&gt;</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></p><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"Fd88i\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>if (window.top !== window.self) {\n    window.top.location = window.self.location;\n}</code></pre><p id=\"ud755b95e\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">局限性</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：攻击者可能通过设置 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">sandbox</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 属性禁用脚本或阻止跳转，因此不能作为唯一防御，只能作为补充。</span></p><h3 id=\"VmPQ5\"><span class=\"ne-text\">总结</span></h3><p id=\"u8cae5385\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">最可靠的防御是在服务器端配置 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">X-Frame-Options</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 或 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">CSP frame-ancestors</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 指令，明确限制哪些网站可以嵌入你的页面。这能从根本上阻止点击劫持攻击。</span></p></div>","body_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"ue7b25a8d\" id=\"ue7b25a8d\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf7fb2cfe\" id=\"uf7fb2cfe\">点击劫持（Clickjacking）</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4a13a05e\" id=\"u4a13a05e\"> 是一种恶意攻击技术，攻击者通过透明或半透明的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u71920b01\" id=\"u71920b01\"><span data-lake-id=\"u41672996\" id=\"u41672996\">&lt;iframe&gt;</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u8e4ef798\" id=\"u8e4ef798\"> 将目标网站覆盖在看似无害的页面上，诱使用户在不知情的情况下点击按钮或链接，从而执行非本意的操作，例如点赞、转账、授权等。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"uxgcc\" id=\"uxgcc\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua5df53dd\" id=\"ua5df53dd\">攻击原理</span></h3><ol list=\"u829a30e2\"><li fid=\"u9af54992\" data-lake-id=\"uce8dfd4e\" id=\"uce8dfd4e\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub110c236\" id=\"ub110c236\">攻击者构建一个恶意页面，并通过 CSS 将目标网站（例如 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u0a3dd3e3\" id=\"u0a3dd3e3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4c697624\" id=\"u4c697624\">bank.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u59d0b220\" id=\"u59d0b220\">）嵌入到一个透明的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u5e6449f8\" id=\"u5e6449f8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u92d59a43\" id=\"u92d59a43\">&lt;iframe&gt;</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u61c6a27c\" id=\"u61c6a27c\"> 中。</span></li><li fid=\"u9af54992\" data-lake-id=\"ub46d68b9\" id=\"ub46d68b9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u508f74ab\" id=\"u508f74ab\">该透明层对准用户可见的诱饵元素（如“点击领奖”按钮）。</span></li><li fid=\"u9af54992\" data-lake-id=\"u9325758c\" id=\"u9325758c\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf959a295\" id=\"uf959a295\">用户点击诱饵时，实际点击的是下方透明的目标网站界面，从而触发了未经授权的操作。</span></li></ol><h3 data-lake-id=\"scZEu\" id=\"scZEu\"><span data-lake-id=\"u31da748c\" id=\"u31da748c\">防范方法</span></h3><h4 data-lake-id=\"FYFhM\" id=\"FYFhM\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2d61db01\" id=\"u2d61db01\">1. 使用 HTTP 响应头</span></h4><ul list=\"ub3e37a6a\"><li fid=\"ud877d987\" data-lake-id=\"uddc5431d\" id=\"uddc5431d\"><code data-lake-id=\"u7eea7046\" id=\"u7eea7046\"><span data-lake-id=\"u63526db2\" id=\"u63526db2\">X-Frame-Options</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ud0c561de\" id=\"ud0c561de\">（传统方案）  </span></li></ul><ul list=\"ub3e37a6a\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"ua03075c9\" data-lake-id=\"u8c0a732f\" id=\"u8c0a732f\"><code data-lake-id=\"u7f33adf2\" id=\"u7f33adf2\"><span data-lake-id=\"u67d7e3bd\" id=\"u67d7e3bd\">DENY</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4e61de2a\" id=\"u4e61de2a\">：禁止所有页面以 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u73ae75c4\" id=\"u73ae75c4\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc4b3f6b0\" id=\"uc4b3f6b0\">&lt;iframe&gt;</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ueda6b530\" id=\"ueda6b530\"> 形式嵌入。  </span></li><li fid=\"ua03075c9\" data-lake-id=\"ub107adac\" id=\"ub107adac\"><code data-lake-id=\"uff17d241\" id=\"uff17d241\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufdbdc2f6\" id=\"ufdbdc2f6\">SAMEORIGIN</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u9ca70b13\" id=\"u9ca70b13\">：仅允许同源页面嵌入。  </span></li><li fid=\"ua03075c9\" data-lake-id=\"u324f5207\" id=\"u324f5207\"><span data-lake-id=\"u75bdafb6\" id=\"u75bdafb6\">示例：</span><code data-lake-id=\"ud880a0d6\" id=\"ud880a0d6\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufe9745ae\" id=\"ufe9745ae\">X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN</span></code></li></ul><ul list=\"ub3e37a6a\" start=\"2\"><li fid=\"ud877d987\" data-lake-id=\"u08abbd21\" id=\"u08abbd21\"><code data-lake-id=\"ue716f24f\" id=\"ue716f24f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6071dcc9\" id=\"u6071dcc9\">Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ud257a604\" id=\"ud257a604\">（现代 CSP 方案，推荐）  </span></li></ul><ul list=\"ub3e37a6a\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"u4b794c92\" data-lake-id=\"u832f3de1\" id=\"u832f3de1\"><span data-lake-id=\"u09e8692b\" id=\"u09e8692b\">可以更精细地控制允许嵌入的父页面。  </span></li><li fid=\"u4b794c92\" data-lake-id=\"ube877a9c\" id=\"ube877a9c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2bfca9f1\" id=\"u2bfca9f1\">示例：</span><code data-lake-id=\"u23a7492d\" id=\"u23a7492d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u995f5626\" id=\"u995f5626\">Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors 'self' https://trusted.com;</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u8ac85431\" id=\"u8ac85431\">  </span></li><li fid=\"u4b794c92\" data-lake-id=\"u8d98e3b5\" id=\"u8d98e3b5\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud958e71a\" id=\"ud958e71a\">该指令支持多个源，比 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u4282e41a\" id=\"u4282e41a\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc8211b22\" id=\"uc8211b22\">X-Frame-Options</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf69ebabc\" id=\"uf69ebabc\"> 更灵活，优先级更高。</span></li></ul><h4 data-lake-id=\"Ua6to\" id=\"Ua6to\"><span data-lake-id=\"u76a68400\" id=\"u76a68400\">2. 前端 frame busting（辅助防御）</span></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u114475ad\" id=\"u114475ad\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8c7abbe4\" id=\"u8c7abbe4\">在页面中添加 JavaScript 代码，尝试检测并跳出 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uc5242c41\" id=\"uc5242c41\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufd779878\" id=\"ufd779878\">&lt;iframe&gt;</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ub7806f6d\" id=\"ub7806f6d\">：</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22if%20(window.top%20!%3D%3D%20window.self)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20window.top.location%20%3D%20window.self.location%3B%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22Fd88i%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"ud755b95e\" id=\"ud755b95e\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7004162a\" id=\"u7004162a\">局限性</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9fb7e719\" id=\"u9fb7e719\">：攻击者可能通过设置 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u12a21f12\" id=\"u12a21f12\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3665c99e\" id=\"u3665c99e\">sandbox</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u3e4868cf\" id=\"u3e4868cf\"> 属性禁用脚本或阻止跳转，因此不能作为唯一防御，只能作为补充。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"VmPQ5\" id=\"VmPQ5\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8824a114\" id=\"u8824a114\">总结</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u8cae5385\" id=\"u8cae5385\"><span data-lake-id=\"u38a050e3\" id=\"u38a050e3\">最可靠的防御是在服务器端配置 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u994f846a\" id=\"u994f846a\"><span data-lake-id=\"u89cf5c82\" id=\"u89cf5c82\">X-Frame-Options</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u77f91800\" id=\"u77f91800\"> 或 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u0a198abc\" id=\"u0a198abc\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6da4ceb4\" id=\"u6da4ceb4\">CSP frame-ancestors</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"udbb1a0bf\" id=\"udbb1a0bf\"> 指令，明确限制哪些网站可以嵌入你的页面。这能从根本上阻止点击劫持攻击。</span></p>","body_draft":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"ue7b25a8d\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">点击劫持（Clickjacking）</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 是一种恶意攻击技术，攻击者通过透明或半透明的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">&lt;iframe&gt;</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 将目标网站覆盖在看似无害的页面上，诱使用户在不知情的情况下点击按钮或链接，从而执行非本意的操作，例如点赞、转账、授权等。</span></p><h3 id=\"uxgcc\"><span class=\"ne-text\">攻击原理</span></h3><ol class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"uce8dfd4e\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">攻击者构建一个恶意页面，并通过 CSS 将目标网站（例如 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">bank.com</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">）嵌入到一个透明的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">&lt;iframe&gt;</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中。</span></li><li id=\"ub46d68b9\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">该透明层对准用户可见的诱饵元素（如“点击领奖”按钮）。</span></li><li id=\"u9325758c\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">用户点击诱饵时，实际点击的是下方透明的目标网站界面，从而触发了未经授权的操作。</span></li></ol><h3 id=\"scZEu\"><span class=\"ne-text\">防范方法</span></h3><h4 id=\"FYFhM\"><span class=\"ne-text\">1. 使用 HTTP 响应头</span></h4><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"uddc5431d\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">X-Frame-Options</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">（传统方案）  </span></li></ul><ul class=\"ne-list-wrap\"><ul ne-level=\"1\" class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u8c0a732f\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">DENY</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：禁止所有页面以 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">&lt;iframe&gt;</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 形式嵌入。  </span></li><li id=\"ub107adac\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">SAMEORIGIN</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：仅允许同源页面嵌入。  </span></li><li id=\"u324f5207\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">示例：</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN</span></code></li></ul></ul><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u08abbd21\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">（现代 CSP 方案，推荐）  </span></li></ul><ul class=\"ne-list-wrap\"><ul ne-level=\"1\" class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u832f3de1\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">可以更精细地控制允许嵌入的父页面。  </span></li><li id=\"ube877a9c\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">示例：</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors 'self' https://trusted.com;</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">  </span></li><li id=\"u8d98e3b5\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">该指令支持多个源，比 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">X-Frame-Options</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 更灵活，优先级更高。</span></li></ul></ul><h4 id=\"Ua6to\"><span class=\"ne-text\">2. 前端 frame busting（辅助防御）</span></h4><p id=\"u114475ad\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在页面中添加 JavaScript 代码，尝试检测并跳出 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">&lt;iframe&gt;</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></p><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"Fd88i\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>if (window.top !== window.self) {\n    window.top.location = window.self.location;\n}</code></pre><p id=\"ud755b95e\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">局限性</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：攻击者可能通过设置 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">sandbox</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 属性禁用脚本或阻止跳转，因此不能作为唯一防御，只能作为补充。</span></p><h3 id=\"VmPQ5\"><span class=\"ne-text\">总结</span></h3><p id=\"u8cae5385\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">最可靠的防御是在服务器端配置 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">X-Frame-Options</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 或 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">CSP frame-ancestors</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 指令，明确限制哪些网站可以嵌入你的页面。这能从根本上阻止点击劫持攻击。</span></p></div>","body_draft_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"ue7b25a8d\" id=\"ue7b25a8d\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf7fb2cfe\" id=\"uf7fb2cfe\">点击劫持（Clickjacking）</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4a13a05e\" id=\"u4a13a05e\"> 是一种恶意攻击技术，攻击者通过透明或半透明的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u71920b01\" id=\"u71920b01\"><span data-lake-id=\"u41672996\" id=\"u41672996\">&lt;iframe&gt;</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u8e4ef798\" id=\"u8e4ef798\"> 将目标网站覆盖在看似无害的页面上，诱使用户在不知情的情况下点击按钮或链接，从而执行非本意的操作，例如点赞、转账、授权等。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"uxgcc\" id=\"uxgcc\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua5df53dd\" id=\"ua5df53dd\">攻击原理</span></h3><ol list=\"u829a30e2\"><li fid=\"u9af54992\" data-lake-id=\"uce8dfd4e\" id=\"uce8dfd4e\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub110c236\" id=\"ub110c236\">攻击者构建一个恶意页面，并通过 CSS 将目标网站（例如 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u0a3dd3e3\" id=\"u0a3dd3e3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4c697624\" id=\"u4c697624\">bank.com</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u59d0b220\" id=\"u59d0b220\">）嵌入到一个透明的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u5e6449f8\" id=\"u5e6449f8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u92d59a43\" id=\"u92d59a43\">&lt;iframe&gt;</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u61c6a27c\" id=\"u61c6a27c\"> 中。</span></li><li fid=\"u9af54992\" data-lake-id=\"ub46d68b9\" id=\"ub46d68b9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u508f74ab\" id=\"u508f74ab\">该透明层对准用户可见的诱饵元素（如“点击领奖”按钮）。</span></li><li fid=\"u9af54992\" data-lake-id=\"u9325758c\" id=\"u9325758c\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf959a295\" id=\"uf959a295\">用户点击诱饵时，实际点击的是下方透明的目标网站界面，从而触发了未经授权的操作。</span></li></ol><h3 data-lake-id=\"scZEu\" id=\"scZEu\"><span data-lake-id=\"u31da748c\" id=\"u31da748c\">防范方法</span></h3><h4 data-lake-id=\"FYFhM\" id=\"FYFhM\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2d61db01\" id=\"u2d61db01\">1. 使用 HTTP 响应头</span></h4><ul list=\"ub3e37a6a\"><li fid=\"ud877d987\" data-lake-id=\"uddc5431d\" id=\"uddc5431d\"><code data-lake-id=\"u7eea7046\" id=\"u7eea7046\"><span data-lake-id=\"u63526db2\" id=\"u63526db2\">X-Frame-Options</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ud0c561de\" id=\"ud0c561de\">（传统方案）  </span></li></ul><ul list=\"ub3e37a6a\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"ua03075c9\" data-lake-id=\"u8c0a732f\" id=\"u8c0a732f\"><code data-lake-id=\"u7f33adf2\" id=\"u7f33adf2\"><span data-lake-id=\"u67d7e3bd\" id=\"u67d7e3bd\">DENY</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4e61de2a\" id=\"u4e61de2a\">：禁止所有页面以 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u73ae75c4\" id=\"u73ae75c4\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc4b3f6b0\" id=\"uc4b3f6b0\">&lt;iframe&gt;</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ueda6b530\" id=\"ueda6b530\"> 形式嵌入。  </span></li><li fid=\"ua03075c9\" data-lake-id=\"ub107adac\" id=\"ub107adac\"><code data-lake-id=\"uff17d241\" id=\"uff17d241\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufdbdc2f6\" id=\"ufdbdc2f6\">SAMEORIGIN</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u9ca70b13\" id=\"u9ca70b13\">：仅允许同源页面嵌入。  </span></li><li fid=\"ua03075c9\" data-lake-id=\"u324f5207\" id=\"u324f5207\"><span data-lake-id=\"u75bdafb6\" id=\"u75bdafb6\">示例：</span><code data-lake-id=\"ud880a0d6\" id=\"ud880a0d6\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufe9745ae\" id=\"ufe9745ae\">X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN</span></code></li></ul><ul list=\"ub3e37a6a\" start=\"2\"><li fid=\"ud877d987\" data-lake-id=\"u08abbd21\" id=\"u08abbd21\"><code data-lake-id=\"ue716f24f\" id=\"ue716f24f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6071dcc9\" id=\"u6071dcc9\">Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ud257a604\" id=\"ud257a604\">（现代 CSP 方案，推荐）  </span></li></ul><ul list=\"ub3e37a6a\" data-lake-indent=\"1\"><li fid=\"u4b794c92\" data-lake-id=\"u832f3de1\" id=\"u832f3de1\"><span data-lake-id=\"u09e8692b\" id=\"u09e8692b\">可以更精细地控制允许嵌入的父页面。  </span></li><li fid=\"u4b794c92\" data-lake-id=\"ube877a9c\" id=\"ube877a9c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2bfca9f1\" id=\"u2bfca9f1\">示例：</span><code data-lake-id=\"u23a7492d\" id=\"u23a7492d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u995f5626\" id=\"u995f5626\">Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors 'self' https://trusted.com;</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u8ac85431\" id=\"u8ac85431\">  </span></li><li fid=\"u4b794c92\" data-lake-id=\"u8d98e3b5\" id=\"u8d98e3b5\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud958e71a\" id=\"ud958e71a\">该指令支持多个源，比 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u4282e41a\" id=\"u4282e41a\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc8211b22\" id=\"uc8211b22\">X-Frame-Options</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf69ebabc\" id=\"uf69ebabc\"> 更灵活，优先级更高。</span></li></ul><h4 data-lake-id=\"Ua6to\" id=\"Ua6to\"><span data-lake-id=\"u76a68400\" id=\"u76a68400\">2. 前端 frame busting（辅助防御）</span></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u114475ad\" id=\"u114475ad\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8c7abbe4\" id=\"u8c7abbe4\">在页面中添加 JavaScript 代码，尝试检测并跳出 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uc5242c41\" id=\"uc5242c41\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufd779878\" id=\"ufd779878\">&lt;iframe&gt;</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ub7806f6d\" id=\"ub7806f6d\">：</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22if%20(window.top%20!%3D%3D%20window.self)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20window.top.location%20%3D%20window.self.location%3B%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22Fd88i%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"ud755b95e\" id=\"ud755b95e\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7004162a\" id=\"u7004162a\">局限性</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9fb7e719\" id=\"u9fb7e719\">：攻击者可能通过设置 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u12a21f12\" id=\"u12a21f12\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3665c99e\" id=\"u3665c99e\">sandbox</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u3e4868cf\" id=\"u3e4868cf\"> 属性禁用脚本或阻止跳转，因此不能作为唯一防御，只能作为补充。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"VmPQ5\" id=\"VmPQ5\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8824a114\" id=\"u8824a114\">总结</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u8cae5385\" id=\"u8cae5385\"><span data-lake-id=\"u38a050e3\" id=\"u38a050e3\">最可靠的防御是在服务器端配置 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u994f846a\" id=\"u994f846a\"><span data-lake-id=\"u89cf5c82\" id=\"u89cf5c82\">X-Frame-Options</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u77f91800\" id=\"u77f91800\"> 或 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u0a198abc\" id=\"u0a198abc\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6da4ceb4\" id=\"u6da4ceb4\">CSP frame-ancestors</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"udbb1a0bf\" id=\"udbb1a0bf\"> 指令，明确限制哪些网站可以嵌入你的页面。这能从根本上阻止点击劫持攻击。</span></p>","word_count":442,"slug":"kxodm2ntd8gx0kty","type":"Doc","title":"什么是点击劫持？如何防范点击劫持？","public":1,"cover":null,"custom_cover":null,"description":"点击劫持（Clickjacking） 是一种恶意攻击技术，攻击者通过透明或半透明的  将目标网站覆盖在看似无害的页面上，诱使用户在不知情的情况下点击按钮或链接，从而执行非本意的操作，例如点赞、转账、授权等。攻击原理攻击者构建一个恶意页面，并通过 CSS 将目标网站（例如 ban...","custom_description":"","format":"lake","status":1,"read_status":1,"editor_meta":"{\"codeblock\":1}","user_id":200222,"created_at":"2026-02-26T08:04:28.000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-06T08:24:07.000Z","published_at":"2026-02-26T08:05:48.000Z","first_published_at":"2026-02-26T08:05:45.927Z","content_updated_at":"2026-02-26T08:05:48.000Z","id":258003755},"doc_digest":"1AyfvAj2gciwDytggPQ-kGmCNVk"}